body: Totally worth every penny.I honestly didn't even needed an earphone at all but reading some reviews did made me go for this one.Given the price I couldn't have asked for anything better. I do have Cx180, Cx275s, XB154AP, Smokin Buds 2, Ink'd and couple of others, but this being at such a cheap price that too with a mic it sure didn't disappointed me. Mids and lows are nice, bass is at least better than my CX180, nicely built, call button works great, wires are not as thin as cx180 which is a bonus cos my cx180 tangles a lot.If anyone is looking for something good without spending much then this one is sure is the one to look and go for.
